{
  "texts": [
    "c is the self-weighted context vector, which has the same dimensions as the hidden state.",
    "W cy,i and b cy,i are the learnable weight and bias for the i th layer in the FNN, respectively (i = 1, 2, 3, and 4).",
    "The attention module for yield collects simulated information of each day from the GRU_basis submodule as input and weighs the contribution of each day's information to the final yield prediction.",
    "Crop annual residue y res can be expressed as:",
    "where GPP t and y Ra,t are the GPP input and predicted Ra at time step t; y yield is the annual predicted yield; and Tx is the number of days in the input time series (in this study Tx = 365)."
